OL,3,CNorth Wales Fire: Whistleblower says
OL,4,Cspeaking out gets you 'blacklisted'
OL,6,FA long-serving officer at has told ITV
OL,7,FNews the organisation has a
OL,8,F"repressive environment" and people
OL,9,Fwho speak out risk being "blacklisted".
OL,11,FIt's after how North Wales Fire and
OL,12,FRescue Service's former assistant
OL,13,Fchief, Stuart Millington, who has been
OL,14,Ftasked with heading up the troubled
OL,15,Fservice in South Wales is himself at
OL,16,Fthe centre of bullying allegations.
OL,18,FThose allegations are due to be heard
OL,19,Fat an employment tribunal in Mold but
OL,20,Fnot until next month. Mr Millington
OL,21,Fdenies the allegations against him.
