OL,6,FAnother employee from North Wales who
OL,7,Ftold us he was too afraid to appear on
OL,8,Fcamera gave us a statement about the
OL,9,Flatest revelations.
OL,11,FHe says: "This has further eroded the
OL,12,Ftrust and confidence of the employees
OL,13,Fin the leadership of the organisation.
OL,15,F"We need a cultural review now, people
OL,16,Fare reluctant to speak out, but we
OL,17,Fwould be queuing up to speak out if
OL,18,Fthe means to do so were safe and
OL,19,Fsupported via a cultural review."
